Package: recon
Type: Package
Title: Useful Functions for Economists
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Christopher", "Mann", email = "cmann3@unl.edu",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 'recon' includes several functions for quickly collecting, viewing,
  and analyzing economic data. Included are functions that collect and search
  data from the Federal Reserve Economic Database and Penn World Tables. 'recon'
  also includes highly customizable plotting solutions for time series data.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
Depends:
    xts,
    zoo
Imports:
    chron,
    dplyr,
    httr,
    jsonlite,
    lmtest,
    lubridate,
    magrittr,
    munsell,
    plyr,
    Rcpp,
    sandwich,
    scales,
    stringr,
    timeDate,
    tis,
    tseries
URL: http://github.com/cmann3/recon
BugReports: http://github.com/cmann3/recon/issues
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
